snippet.title: Fetch Quest - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
You are dog. Climb fast. Save your best friend.
Play the game for free here: https://lumpytouch.itch.io/fetch-quest
Complete Playthrough: COMING SOON
Soundtrack Playlist: COMING SOON

The Fetch Quest Team:
Lumpy: Art - https://twitter.com/LumpyTouch
jf1x: Programming - https://twitter.com/jf1x_
Larner: Music - https://twitter.com/LarnerMusic

This game would NOT have been possible without support from my Patreon Pals. If you want to help me make projects like this, any pledge helps me a LOT! https://www.patreon.com/LumpyTouch

Thumbnail art by Goosyberry: https://twitter.com/goosyberry

Let us know what you think about the game!

#trailer #indie #game
